sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(39, 174, 96) Storefront
        participant Customer as Customer
        participant Portal as Return Portal (Yves)
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker Backend
        participant Returns as Return Management
        participant OMS as OMS (return states)
        participant Cmd as Custom Carrier Command
    end
    box rgb(149, 165, 166) External
        participant Carrier as DHL / DPD / GLS
        participant Talend as Talend → ERP
    end

    Customer->>Portal: Open return portal, select items
    Note over Portal: Items must be Shipped/Delivered & within return policy
    Portal->>Returns: Create return
    Returns->>OMS: Move items to "Waiting for return"
    OMS->>Cmd: Fire carrier-label command (on transition)
    Cmd->>Carrier: Request return label/voucher [REST]
    Carrier-->>Cmd: Return label
    Cmd-->>Customer: Provide label
    OMS->>OMS: Returned → Refunded
    OMS->>Talend: Export return/refund state
